com.vanillasource.gerec

Interface AcceptMediaType<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MediaType<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteArrayAcceptType, LineBasedCollectionType, PolymorphicTypes, SameTypeAlternatives

    public interface AcceptMediaType<T>
    The part of a media-type for receiving the given type. This includes adding the necessary modifications to a request, as parsing it in the response.

    • Method Summary
